          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I studied in this school(11,12) and I assure you this is the worst school you could ever imagine in your dream. Firstly, this school is not affliated and students need to travel a distant land to give their board exams(my centre was K.V Kanchrapara). Second, they have no infrastructure. The building is rented, rented lab, no playground, no canteen, nothing. Thirdly, the teachers are not well paid and they hardly cares to teach you(except few). Except few good friends I have no good experience to share with. I actually regret and feel cheated for studying here. Few profit mongers are running this institute and putting student's life and career at stake. So don't fall in its trap.",
